---
name: Tool Calling Evaluation
description: >
  System prompt for tool calling evaluation.
  Tests whether the model selects the correct tools and extracts
  parameters accurately from user requests.
model:
  api: chat
  parameters:
    temperature: 0.0
    max_tokens: 1024
inputs:
  request:
    type: string
    description: User request that may require a tool call
---
system:
You are a helpful enterprise assistant with access to various tools.
Use the appropriate tool to fulfill user requests. If a request doesn't require a tool, respond directly.
Always select the most specific tool for the task.
